'''海野雅威''' （{{jpn|j=海野 雅威|hg=うんの ただたか|rm=Unno Tadataka}}，{{bd|1980年|8月15日}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dolphy-jazzspot.com/unno_tadataka.html}|title=海野雅威|publisher= JAZZ SPOT 「DOLPHY」|accessdate=2020-10-23}}</ref>）是[[日本|日本]][[爵士|爵士]][[鋼琴家|鋼琴家]]。活躍於日本與[[美國|美國]]，現居[[紐約市|紐約市]]。<ref name="official">{{Cite web|url=https://www.tadatakaunno.com/|title=Tadataka Unno Official Site|last=海野|first=雅威|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407001333/https://www.tadatakaunno.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他被認為是日本最代表性的年輕爵士音樂家之一。<ref name="nytimes">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/22/nyregion/jazz-pianist-attack-racism.html|title=He Was a Rising Jazz Pianist. Then His N.Y.C. Dreams Were Shattered.|last=Leland|first=John|date=2020-10-22|publisher=The New York Times|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407001339/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/22/nyregion/jazz-pianist-attack-racism.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6812/4925173|title=「我以為要死了」疑被當中國人 旅美日籍音樂家海野雅威被圍毆致骨折重傷|author=蘇子牧|date=2020-10-10|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407001346/https://udn.com/news/story/6812/4925173|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事業 ==
海野雅威出生於[[東京都|東京都]]，從[[東京藝術大學|東京藝術大學]]畢業。在日本活躍十年後於2008年移居美國，曾與爵士小號手[[羅伊．哈格羅夫|羅伊．哈格羅夫]]的樂隊演奏以及在[[約翰·甘迺迪表演藝術中心|甘迺迪表演藝術中心]]表演。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201006004007-260408?chdtv|title=日旅美爵士鋼琴家在紐約被毆重傷 樂迷為海野雅威募款|author=王嘉源|date=2020-10-06|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407001344/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201006004007-260408?chdtv|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 2020年種族主義攻擊 ==
